<span class="comment"><font color=#000000>"Yes, totally. I'll get some facts about xyz and get
 back to you, so you can choose the best thing for the team."<p>The manager comeback to that is:<p><pre><code>  Manager: Fine, but let's put the fact-finding on the back burner as it's not a high priority right now.</code></pre></font></span><p><font size=1><font color=#f6f6ef>-----</font></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table border=0><tr><td><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/s.gif" height=1 width=120></td><td valign=top><center><a id=up_2337173 href="vote?for=2337173&dir=up&whence=%2f%78%3f%66%6e%69%64%3d%62%71%71%62%65%6f%5a%49%30%56"><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/grayarrow.gif" border=0 vspace=3 hspace=2></a><span id=down_2337173></span></center></td><td class="default"><div style="margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:-10px; "><span class="comhead"><a href="user?id=d0m">d0m</a> 325 days ago  | <a href="item?id=2337173">link</a></span></div><br>
